<div class="floating-elements" id="floating"></div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>My Sweet Princess 👑</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">From your brother with endless love 💖</p>
  </div>

  <div class="icons">
    💖 &nbsp; 💅 &nbsp; ☕ &nbsp; ✨ &nbsp; 🌸 &nbsp; 💅 &nbsp; 💖
  </div>

  <!-- Complete Long Message -->
  <div class="big-message">
    <p>
      Pata nahi kyu, par mujhe tumse hamesha ek apnapan feel hua… ek behen wali
      feeling. Shayad tumhe kabhi meri taraf se woh bond feel na hua ho, aur ho
      sakta hai meri kuch baatein ya behaviour bhi tumhe ajeeb lage ho. Par jo
      bhi tha, dil se mera intention hamesha saaf tha.<br /><br />

      Mujhe pata hai rishte sirf bol dene se nahi bante. Time lagta hai, trust
      lagta hai, feelings lagti hai. Aur trust especially kisi ladke par karna
      easy nahi hota, ye baat main samajhta hu. Isliye maine kabhi force nahi
      kiya ki tum mujhe bhai mano. Main bas naturally woh relation feel karta
      hu.<br /><br />

      Sach bolu toh kabhi kabhi bura zarur lagta hai… jab tum ignore karti ho,
      avoid karti ho, ya aisa feel hota hai jaise meri koi importance hi nahi.
      Main bhi insaan hu, mere paas bhi dil hai. Aur haan, mujhe ye bhi pata hai
      ki shayad main tumhe zarurat se zyada attention deta hu.<br /><br />

      Agar main chahta toh planning, tricks, ya fake behaviour use karke tumhare
      saath ek “better image” bana leta. But tumhare saath main kabhi waise act
      nahi karna chahta tha. Mujhe fake relation nahi chahiye tha. Isliye maine
      hamesha dil se behave kiya, bina kisi game ke.<br /><br />

      Aur ek baat clear karna chahta hu… agar tumhe kabhi bhi mere intentions ko
      leke doubt hua ho, toh please woh galat hai. Main genuinely tumhe apni
      behen maanta hu, aur hamesha wahi respect aur care rahegi.<br /><br />

      Tum mujhe bhai mano ya na mano, woh tumhari feelings hai aur main uski
      respect karta hu. Bas meri taraf se jo rishta hai, woh hamesha genuine
      rahega. Aur kabhi bhi life me tumhe meri zarurat pade — main bina soche
      tumhare saath rahunga.<br /><br />

      Aaj nahi toh shayad kabhi future me tum meri feelings samjho… aur dil se
      mujhe apna bhai mano. Mere liye wahi kaafi hoga.<br /><br />

      <strong style="color: var(--dark-pink); font-size: 1.4rem">
        I love you, behen. Hamesha se aur hamesha ke liye 💖
      </strong>
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Audio Player -->
  <div class="audio-container">
    <h3 style="color: var(--hot-pink); margin-bottom: 15px">
      🎵 Dil Se Suno...
    </h3>
    <audio id="loveAudio" controls autoplay loop>
      <source src="/assets/dil.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
    </audio>
  </div>

  <!-- Message Form -->

    <div class="form-section">
      <h2 style="color: var(--dark-pink)">
        💌 Tumhare Pyare Bhaiya ko Message Likho
      </h2>
      <p class="tip">Tum multiple messages bhej sakti ho one after one💖 tbhi niche wala button kaam krega</p>

      <form id="msgForm" action="/ishh/msgtome" method="POST">
        <textarea
          name="message"
          id="message"
          placeholder="Bhaiya, dil ki baat likho yahan..."
          required
        ></textarea
        ><br />
        <button type="submit" class="send-btn">
          Send Message to Bhaiya 💌
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <button onclick="goForward()" class="forward-btn" id="forwardBtn">
      Chlo Mere Pyare Bhaiya, Ab Aage Badhte Hai ✨
    </button>
  </div>

  <script>
    const hasSubmitted = <%= hasSubmittedMessage ? 'true' : 'false' %>;

    // Floating Animation
    function createFloating() {
      const emojis = ["💖", "💅", "☕", "✨", "🌸", "🦋", "💗"];
      const span = document.createElement("span");
      span.textContent = emojis[Math.floor(Math.random() * emojis.length)];
      span.style.position = "absolute";
      span.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + "%";
      span.style.fontSize = (Math.random() * 2.2 + 2.2) + "rem";
      span.style.animation = `floatUp ${Math.random() * 10 + 12}s linear infinite`;
      span.style.opacity = Math.random() * 0.75 + 0.6;
      document.getElementById("floating").appendChild(span);
      setTimeout(() => span.remove(), 35000);
    }

    setInterval(createFloating, 250);
    for (let i = 0; i < 15; i++) setTimeout(createFloating, i * 180);

    // Auto Play Audio
    window.addEventListener("load", () => {
      document.getElementById("loveAudio").play().catch(() => {});
    });

    function goForward() {
      if (!hasSubmitted) {
        alert("💖 Princess, pehle ek message toh bhejo apne bhaiya ko...\nBina message ke aage nahi ja sakte.");
        return;
      }
      window.location.href = "/ishh/secret";
    }


    // Floating animation keyframe
    const style = document.createElement("style");
    style.innerHTML = `@keyframes floatUp { 0% { transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(0deg); } 100% { transform: translateY(-120vh) rotate(720deg); } }`;
    document.head.appendChild(style);
  </script>
</div>
